the daily by upper classmen.

00:13:37.450 --> 00:13:41.930
And it was because he
was perceived as queer.

00:13:41.930 --> 00:13:45.470
And for the first
time I responded

00:13:45.470 --> 00:13:51.050
to a situation levelheaded,
removed him, reported it.

00:13:51.050 --> 00:13:56.880
And that day when I got home,
I wrote up our guidelines,

00:13:56.880 --> 00:14:00.020
I recruited our sponsor,
and a week later we

00:14:00.020 --> 00:14:00.990
had a club in motion.

00:14:00.990 --> 00:14:04.460
Like, that's what I'm
proudest of is just response.

00:14:04.460 --> 00:14:06.570
FEMALE SPEAKER: OK.

00:14:06.570 --> 00:14:08.070
STEPHANIE FROSCH:
That's incredible.

00:14:08.070 --> 00:14:09.610
Sorry. [INAUDIBLE]
not from that.

