00:15:32.992 --> 00:15:33.950
Now I'm at this school.

00:15:33.950 --> 00:15:35.030
Now I have this partner.

00:15:35.030 --> 00:15:37.380
Now I have this
relationship with my peers.

00:15:37.380 --> 00:15:40.240
