pretend it didn't happen.

00:16:34.470 --> 00:16:35.630
You don't have to
pretend it's better.

00:16:35.630 --> 00:16:37.020
But you can grow from it.

00:16:37.020 --> 00:16:39.380
You can make something
positive afterwards.

00:16:39.380 --> 00:16:41.910
And just remember that
every negative experience

00:16:41.910 --> 00:16:43.790
