vulnerability is weakness.

00:18:35.570 --> 00:18:38.000
But really it's allowing
yourself the strength to feel.

00:18:38.000 --> 00:18:41.080
So if something
isn't going your way,

00:18:41.080 --> 00:18:44.500
whether it's an event or
situation, you can grow in it.

00:18:47.220 --> 00:18:49.170
MARS HALLMAN: Well, my
